BUSINESS MODEL & SYSTEM SPECIFICATION v2.0

AI-Assisted Tax Surplus / Excess Proceeds Recovery Platform (USA)

0. EXECUTIVE SUMMARY (UPDATED – IT / ARCHITECT GPT)

Ovo je high-compliance, audit-first, attorney-executed platforma koja asistira u recovery-ju tax surplus / excess proceeds sredstava u SAD.

Ključna korekcija u v2.0
Platforma nikada ne funkcioniše bez advokatskog izvršnog sloja.
Sav payout i monetizacija se dešavaju isključivo kroz attorney-managed flow.

Platforma ostaje:
    • UPL-safe by design
    • Human-in-the-loop
    • AI-assisted, nikad AI-deciding

1. SYSTEM GOALS & NON-GOALS (REVIDIRANO)

1.1 Ciljevi sistema (hard)

✔ Identifikacija potencijalnih CA surplus slučajeva
✔ Operativna klasifikacija (Tier A/B/C)
✔ Claim package priprema (non-legal)
✔ Legal execution routing ka advokatu
✔ Monetizacija isključivo kroz attorney fee realization
✔ Potpuna auditabilnost (case + fee)

1.2 Non-Goals (prošireno)

❌ Platforma nikada:
    • ne prima sredstva
    • ne kontroliše trust account
    • ne isplaćuje fee direktno od vlasnika
    • ne zatvara slučaj bez attorney confirmation

2. DUAL OPERATING MODES (NOVO – KLJUČNA IZMENU)

2.1 Mode A – Platform-Led (Phase 1 default)

Flow
Platforma:
    • discovery
    • triage
    • client consent
    • claim package

Advokat:
    • filing
    • trust account
    • payout
    • fee realization

Hard rule

No Attorney Assigned → No Payout Phase

Svaki case mora imati:
    • AttorneyExecutionPath = REQUIRED

2.2 Mode B – Attorney-Led SaaS

Advokat:
    • koristi platformu kao:
        ◦ discovery engine
        ◦ case management
        ◦ compliance-safe ops layer

Platforma:
    • nema direktan B2C odnos
    • monetizuje isključivo B2B

3. JURISDICTION SCOPE (UPDATED)

Phase 1 (MVP)
    • State: California ONLY
    • Counties: konfigurisani (≤10 u startu)
    • Tier A + deo Tier B
    • Bez automatizovanog filing-a

Phase 2
    • Multi-state expansion
    • Optional fix fee za high-volume firms

Phase 3
    • Federal coverage
    • Mandatory fix + reduced fee

4. CORE MODULE UPDATES (SAMO IZMENJENO)

4.1 Case Management – Legal Execution Extension

Novi obavezni atributi case-a:
{
  "legal_execution_mode": "ATTORNEY_PARTNER | ATTORNEY_CLIENT_OWNED",
  "assigned_attorney_id": "...",
  "expected_payout_window": "...",
  "closure_confirmation_required": true
}
Bez ova 3 polja → case ne može preći u PAYOUT_CONFIRMED.

4.2 Payout & Billing Engine (REVIDIRANO)

Phase 1 Pricing Rule (California)
    • Platform fee = 12%
    • Osnovica = realizovani attorney fee
    • Fix fee = 0
PlatformFee = AttorneyFee * 0.12
Trigger:
    • Attorney payout confirmation
    • Trust disbursement summary upload

5. FEE CONTROL & LOCK-IN MECHANISMS (NOVO)

5.1 Case Origination Lock (Contract + System)

Case koji je:
    • discovered
    • triaged
    • prepared

na platformi → mora biti zatvoren na platformi.

5.2 Progressive Feature Lock

Ako postoji:
    • neconfirmiran payout
    • overdue case (beyond expected window)

→ advokat gubi:
    • discovery feed
    • batch ops
    • new case intake

5.3 Closure Enforcement

Bez:
    • payout amount
    • attorney fee
    • trust confirmation

→ case status = BLOCKED

6. CUSTOMER SEGMENTS (UPDATED)

Primary (Phase 1)
    • Licensed California attorneys / law firms

Secondary
    • Bivši vlasnici (isključivo kroz attorney rail)

7. TECH STACK (UNCHANGED)

(ostaje identično kao u v1 – nema potrebe za izmenama)

8. EXECUTION PLAN (UPDATED)

Phase 0 – Legal Hardening (CA-only)
    • California surplus rules
    • Attorney agreement (Phase 1)
    • Fee cap validation

Phase 1 – Platform Core
    • Case lifecycle
    • Attorney routing
    • Fee ledger

Phase 2 – AI Assist
    • Parsing
    • Tier suggestions
    • Missing doc detection

9. SUCCESS METRICS (REVIDIRANO)
    • Realized attorney fee
    • Platform fee collected
    • Case leakage rate = 0
    • Off-platform closure attempts = 0
    • Regulatory incidents = 0

10. STRATEGIC CONCLUSION (IMPORTANT)

Ova v2.0 verzija:

✔ ne menja DNK platforme
✔ rešava naplatu
✔ rešava scale
✔ rešava UPL rizik
✔ uvodi jasan upgrade path (fix fee kasnije)

